Changes in Version 0.3
------------------------------------------
Date: 2024-11-28
* Change the package name from ggradar to ggradar2.
* Add ggradar2.r function cloned from https://github.com/pedrosdr/ggradar/tree/ggradar2, with some minor adjustments made.
* Build ggradar.Rd and ggradar2.Rd files for better understanding the usages of ggradar and ggradar2 function.
* Fixed some known issues.
* Update the DESCRIPTION file.
* Update the README file.
* Add the NEWS file.


